Clockwise from top: <a href="/wiki/Trench_warfare" title="Trench warfare">Trenches</a> on the <a href="/wiki/Western_Front" title="Western Front">Western Front</a>; a <a href="/wiki/United_Kingdom_of_Great_Britain_and_Ireland" title="United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland">British</a> <a href="/wiki/Mark_IV_tank" title="Mark IV tank" class="mw-redirect">Mark IV tank</a> crossing a trench; <a href="/wiki/Royal_Navy" title="Royal Navy">Royal Navy</a> <a href="/wiki/Battleship" title="Battleship">battleship</a> <a href="/wiki/HMS_Irresistible_(1898)" title="HMS Irresistible (1898)">HMS <i>Irresistible</i></a> sinking after striking a <a href="/wiki/Naval_mine" title="Naval mine">mine</a> at the <a href="/wiki/Naval_operations_in_the_Dardanelles_Campaign" title="Naval operations in the Dardanelles Campaign">Battle of the Dardanelles</a>; a <a href="/wiki/Vickers_machine_gun" title="Vickers machine gun">Vickers machine gun</a> crew with <a href="/wiki/Gas_mask" title="Gas mask">gas masks</a>, and German <a href="/wiki/Albatros_D.III" title="Albatros D.III">Albatros D.III</a> <a href="/wiki/Biplane" title="Biplane">biplanes</a></td>
